    <item>
      <title>Prework</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/collection/prework/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Jan 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/collection/prework/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the &#xD;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/&#34;&gt;Introducing Yourself Online&lt;/a&gt; workshop! We look forward to meeting you. Before attending the workshop, please complete the following prework.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;set-up-rstudio-cloud&#34;&gt;Set up RStudio Cloud&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#set-up-rstudio-cloud&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;anchor-symbol&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; height=&#34;26&#34; width=&#34;26&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 22 22&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76.0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71.0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71.0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76.0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Sign up for a free RStudio Cloud account at &#xD;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://rstudio.cloud/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;https://rstudio.cloud/&lt;/a&gt; before the workshop. I recommend logging in with an existing Google or GitHub account, if you have one (rather than creating a new account with another password you have to remember). I want you to be able to work from your own laptop in this workshop, but Cloud is an important back-up plan should you run into troubles.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>A postcard</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/collection/day01/02-postcards/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Jan 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/collection/day01/02-postcards/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;pre-requisites&#34;&gt;Pre-requisites&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#pre-requisites&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;anchor-symbol&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; height=&#34;26&#34; width=&#34;26&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 22 22&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76.0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71.0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71.0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76.0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;First, make sure you have the latest version of the postcards package installed from CRAN:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;install.packages(&amp;#34;postcards&amp;#34;)&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Restart your R session. If you use RStudio, use the menu item &lt;em&gt;Session &amp;gt; Restart R&lt;/em&gt; or the associated keyboard shortcut:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;Ctrl + Shift + F10&lt;/kbd&gt; (Windows and Linux) or&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;Command + Shift + F10&lt;kbd&gt; (Mac OS).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;packageVersion(&amp;#34;postcards&amp;#34;)&#xD;&#xA;[1] ‘0.2.0’&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;create-github-repo&#34;&gt;Create GitHub repo&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#create-github-repo&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;anchor-symbol&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; height=&#34;26&#34; width=&#34;26&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 22 22&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76.0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71.0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71.0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76.0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Online.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
